replies.body:
Hey Riot, $32 says you wont read the comment, but a quick suggestion from me (and most likely others) is to include a "Log out" switch.  Ya know, so people with multiple accounts don't have to go through the hastle (myself not included).  I can see why it could become bothersome.  Also, an option to mute pingers.  We have the ability to mute players, but they can still ping like total dicks.  And I know you'll be thinking "Well yeah, sure they are annoying, but what if they really do need a blue flag assist?"  Another idea would be to continuously lower the maximum pings if they reach that bar (From a total of 8 to a total of 7, so on and so forth).  Don't tell us you're gonna do that, because trolls will work around it, but just an idea.  Another great idea: Make a free skin rotation?  I'd like to believe that would increase consumer buying of skins (A couple of marketing classes under my belt)

TL;DR:  Log out button, ways to mute excessive pingers, skin rotations.

Thank you, and thanks for being such a great company.  Cheers! {{champion:62}}
